    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-809e-a030-fbc5987d8ead",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Groups based on Collaborative Learning Flow Patterns often lead to good outcomes. While forming groups based on pedagogical guidelines, time and complexity often prevent the formation of optimal groups. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-809e-a030-fbc5987d8ead",
        "parent": {
